She did, so she got arrested. Somehow, the Spanish took her to a party and then released her

data.text: @LKost09 That was in 1830, IIRC. She was there with Vere and Lady Stuart de Rothesay. The only thing she was asked was not to set foot in Spain. She did, got arrested, taken to a party, and returned the following day. Then was scolded for that by the Rothesays.
